[Theses reports appear to record sporadic outbreaks of mumps virus
infection unconnected to the major outbreak originating in New York
state. The New York state outbreak subsequently spreading to adjacent
states and eventually abroad to Quebec and Israel, mainly through the
movement of students attending Yeshiva schools.

